{
  "texts": [
    "Libraries were constructed from circularized cDNA using the same primers as for tRNASeq.",
    "Amplification was performed using KAPA HiFi DNA polymerase (Roche) in 1×HiFi buffer with an initial denaturation at 95 °C for 3 min, followed by 6-10 cycles of 98 °C for 20 s, 62 °C for 30 s and 72 °C for 15 s at a ramp rate of 3 °C s -1.",
    "The PCR products were purified by size selection on an 8% polyacrylamide and 1×TBE gel.",
    "Excised gel slices were crushed with a pestle and DNA was eluted by rotating samples overnight in 300 µl DNA elution buffer (300 nM NaCl, 10 mM Tris-HCl pH 7.5 and 0.2% Triton X-100).",
    "After ethanol precipitation, the libraries were quantified using a Qubit dsDNA high sensitivity kit and 75-86-bp single-end sequencing was performed on an Illumina NextSeq 500 platform, generating >19 × 10 6 reads per library."
  ]
}